  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OUR NEW GAME!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/9f9c8b6c8ab77a49466818a621328aef.poster.avif?t=1728849020\" width=600 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/9f9c8b6c8ab77a49466818a621328aef.webm?t=1728849020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRO... TO... RO... GROTORO!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GROTORO is a multiplayer couch space globular fatty nervous farting bull brawl in space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reflex, timing, precision, courage, endurance, tactics, feints, coalitions, treachery, charisma, tenacity, manipulation, power... Here are all the qualities you must have to be the greasiest Grotoro!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/f6ae1523fdd058890f18556685fa6138.poster.avif?t=1728849020\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/f6ae1523fdd058890f18556685fa6138.webm?t=1728849020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 players epic battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with AI if you don't have enough friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed control Blobby Volley style: from 50% to 200%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully editable controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the \"Yaaa\" (dash) to hurt and kill your opponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the \"Olé\" to dodge opponents attacks...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bounce on screen borders to hit them with style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide behind your fat balls to trick other players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash into others Grotoros' dash to perform an epic counter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bouncy interface</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instant fun: 0 tuto, 0 story, 0 loading</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the last and greasiest Grotoro!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who let the bulls out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who, Who, Who, Who, WHO?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recommandation: best played with X360 or XOne gamepad!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Design & Programing by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@MatoLabu</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visuals, Music & Sound by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@Tomavatars</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guest:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D bulls modeling by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@retmia from @ImmaterialStu</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/9f9c8b6c8ab77a49466818a621328aef.poster.avif?t=1728849020\" width=600 height=195 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/9f9c8b6c8ab77a49466818a621328aef.webm?t=1728849020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRO... TO... RO... GROTORO!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GROTORO is a multiplayer couch space globular fatty nervous farting bull brawl in space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reflex, timing, precision, courage, endurance, tactics, feints, coalitions, treachery, charisma, tenacity, manipulation, power... Here are all the qualities you must have to be the greasiest Grotoro!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/f6ae1523fdd058890f18556685fa6138.poster.avif?t=1728849020\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/825580/extras/f6ae1523fdd058890f18556685fa6138.webm?t=1728849020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 players epic battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with AI if you don't have enough friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed control Blobby Volley style: from 50% to 200%</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully editable controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the \"Yaaa\" (dash) to hurt and kill your opponents</p></li><li><p class=\